additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Pie Filling (55%) [Beef, Water, Thickener (1422), Seasoning (Salt, Wheat Flour, Hydrolysed Vegetable Protein, Spices, Dehydrated Vegetables, Canola Oil), Natural Colour (Caramel I)], Pastry (45%) [Wheat Flour, Margarine (Animal Fats, Vegetable Oil (Palm, Canola), Water, Salt, Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin, 471 - Palm), Acidity Regulators (331, 330), Antioxidant (307b -Soy), Natural Colour (Carotene), Natural Flavouring), Water, Salt, Mineral Salts (Sodium Carbonate, 341), Emulsifier (481 - Palm), Thickener (412), Pastry Glaze [Mineral Salts (Sodium Carbonate, 451), Maltodextrin (Wheat), Sugar, Thickener (415), Natural Colour (Annatto)]. Party Pie contains 23% beef.
